Help guards

Guards are only way of denying access from various players into
castles. Guards can be bought from castle shop, located (not yet).

Guards are not aggressive, but they will attack with group if
they fall under attack, or someone starts breaking things apart.
They will also notify their owner from previous actions.

Commands:

morph <guard> - morphs guard back to figurine.
order <guard> to <command> <arg> - order guard.
	command : block - set blocking direction to <arg>
		  allow - add <arg> to friends list
		  ban - remove <arg> from friends list
		  list - list players on friends list
info <guard> - to see guard's name and level.
	

See also 'help figurines' and 'help castles'
